#  EXP 10 (Subqueries + Joins)

### 1. Display names of employees from dept 10 with salary greater than ANY employee in other departments

```sql id="e10q1"
SELECT ENAME FROM Employee WHERE DeptNo=10 AND SAL>ANY(SELECT SAL FROM Employee WHERE DeptNo<>10);
```

### 2. Display names of employees from dept 10 with salary greater than ALL employees in other departments

```sql id="e10q2"
SELECT ENAME FROM Employee WHERE DeptNo=10 AND SAL>ALL(SELECT SAL FROM Employee WHERE DeptNo<>10);
```

