### 5. Display employees whose manager name is JONES

```sql id="e10q5"
SELECT E.ENAME FROM Employee E JOIN Employee M ON E.MGR=M.EMPNO WHERE M.ENAME='JONES';
```

### 6. Display ename who are working in sales dept

```sql id="e10q6"
SELECT ENAME FROM Employee WHERE DeptNo=(SELECT DeptNo FROM Department WHERE Dname='SALES');
```

